729
00:53:21,672 --> 00:53:22,848
Hei, Kamu.

730
00:53:23,583 --> 00:53:24,658
Ya?

731
00:53:31,152 --> 00:53:33,098
Baiklah. Terima kasih.

732
00:53:35,852 --> 00:53:39,122
