751
00:54:26,372 --> 00:54:27,372
"PJT"?

752
00:54:27,372 --> 00:54:29,088
Pemakai baju terburuk.

753
00:54:29,672 --> 00:54:32,083
Astaga. Lihat pakaiannya.

